<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Breakthrough Cathedral</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #046307;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .greeting {
            color: #046307;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #046307;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #046307;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .event-card {
            background-color: #f0f7f0;
            border-left: 4px solid #046307;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .scripture {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #046307;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8fcf8;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Breakthrough Cathedral</h1>
        <p>Growing in Faith, Serving in Love</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
            Welcome, <span class="highlight"><%= firstname %> <%= lastname %>!</span>
        </div>
        
        <p>We are absolutely thrilled to welcome you to our church family! It's a joy to have you join us on this faith journey.</p>
        
        <div class="scripture">
            "For where two or three gather in my name, there am I with them."<br>
            <strong>- Matthew 18:20</strong>
        </div>
        
        <h2>This Week's Highlights</h2>
        
        <div class="event-card">
            <h3>📖 Sunday Worship Service</h3>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM</p>
            <p><strong>Message:</strong> "Walking in Faith Through Uncertain Times"</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Main Sanctuary</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="event-card">
            <h3>🙏 Wednesday Prayer Gathering</h3>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> 7:00 PM</p>
            <p><strong>Focus:</strong> Community Prayer & Support</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Chapel Room</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Get Connected</h2>
        <p>We'd love to help you get plugged into our community:</p>
        
        <p>
            <a href="https://yourchurchwebsite.com/small-groups" class="button">
                Join a Small Group
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <p>
            <a href="https://yourchurchwebsite.com/volunteer" class="button">
                Volunteer Opportunities
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <h2>Stay Updated</h2>
        <p>This newsletter will be sent monthly with updates, events, and spiritual encouragement. Be sure to add us to your contacts to ensure you receive our emails!</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Breakthrough Cathedral</strong></p>
            <p>123 Faith Avenue, Your City, State 12345</p>
            <p>Phone: (555) 123-4567 | Email: info@breakthroughcathedral.org</p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://yourchurchwebsite.com" style="color: #046307;">Website</a> | 
                <a href="https://facebook.com/yourchurch" style="color: #046307;">Facebook</a> | 
                <a href="https://youtube.com/yourchurch" style="color: #046307;">YouTube</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                You're receiving this email because you expressed interest in Breakthrough Cathedral.<br>
                <a href="https://yourchurchwebsite.com/unsubscribe" style="color: #666;">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                <a href="https://yourchurchwebsite.com/preferences" style="color: #666;">Update Preferences</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>